/*
1. Initialize deck
 -shuffle

2. Deal cards to player and dealer (function dealingInitialCards(deck))
 -initialize two empty array -> playerCards and dealerCards
 -display player's two cards (function displayCards(playerCards)) //use default parameter
 and dealer's first card (function displayCards(dealerCards, 0))

3. Player turn: hit or stay (while loop)
   -ask if they want to hit or stay (function askingHitOrStay(msg)) 
   -if hit (function pickingOneCard(deck)) / (function addingCard(playerCards))
   -display cards every time (function displayCards(playerCards))
   -check if bust every time  (function busted(playerCards))

   - repeat until bust or stay
   
4. If player bust, dealer wins.

5. Dealer turn: (while loop)
show dealers all cards  (function displayCards(dealerCards))
type anything to move next (function nextStep(msg))
pickingOneCard(deck)) / (function addingCard(dealerCards))
repeat until total >= 17 (function biggerThanSeventeen(dealerCards))
check if bust every time  (function busted(playerCards))
6. If dealer busts, player wins.

7. Compare cards and declare winner. 
(function detectWinner(playerCards, dealerCards)) and (function displayWinner())



data structure for cards (card deck, player, dealer)

2 3 4 5 6 7 8 9 10 - face value
J Q K              - 10
ACE                - 1 or 11

*/
